{"tid":1652938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行政長官對克魯茲不見暴力行為表示匪夷所思　指政客不應肆意批評香港","createTime":"2019-10-14T01:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T01:58:00.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4752321400401a35442695834b98cf7b91de0973","tid":1652938,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:11:11.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官辦公室發聲明，反駁美國共和黨參議員克魯茲。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，尊重外國政客發表言論的自由，但言論應以事實為基礎，又指傳媒已報道香港發生的暴力破壞行為，對克魯茲表示未見示威者的暴力行為實在匪夷所思。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指，政客發表言論前，應思考如果同樣情況發生在自己國家會如何處理，政客不應不負責任地肆意批評香港，甚至以不同方式表達對暴力行為的支持或認同，又說行政長官因另有公務取消與克魯茲會面，而克魯茲之前對閉門會議安排並沒有異議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=366102&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366102%26refer%3D&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN%2FroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=ef393381\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366102%26refer%3D&h=dae52e53\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=366102&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"ac0da259d73c4e331a11fbd87220d6be3ab856f1","tid":1652938,"uid":271894,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"係啦 係啦 全世界得你岩 <br />\n其他人都係錯既"},{"pid":"2a85865fed37b2656ace35275bf4521b7ef48510","tid":1652938,"uid":123738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:15:54.000Z","msg":"黑警做果d美帝梗係分到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那野玩手段只不過係低能級別"},{"pid":"e3af1410e99435b32f4802b06b521a4eb25630ad","tid":1652938,"uid":47850,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"美國內政不容許中國說三道四"},{"pid":"95e9efbecaa52249ce51c79a7f9062b357a712c2","tid":1652938,"uid":99962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:20:18.000Z","msg":"林鄭唔係間諜真係冇人信， 步步特登行錯之餘又迎合中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi